com.mindfusion.charting

Class PieRadarRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.charting.SeriesRenderer
      • com.mindfusion.charting.RadarRenderer
        • com.mindfusion.charting.PieRadarRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataChangedListener, SeriesContainer, com.mindfusion.common.ObservableListListener<Series>, java.util.EventListener

    public class PieRadarRenderer
extends RadarRenderer
    A SeriesRenderer that draws pie-radars, where data items are represented by circular sectors of equal central angles, and the sector corresponding to a data item has radius proportional to its value.
